    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>坐上指挥席位 — 带领你的坦克乘员走向胜利。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Iron Fist</i> 让你藏身于二战最具标志性的钢铁战车之中，通过完整的第三人称直接操控，以全新的方式体验战场。每一次扣动扳机、每一次变速、每一次装甲被击中都显得格外个人化、极具冲击力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指挥传奇坦克，带领老练乘员，一发炮弹一发炮弹地改写二战经典战役的结局。Iron Fist 在提供紧张刺激的装甲战同时，依旧保留了 Men of War 所标志的战术深度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个扩展包从装甲兵的视角重新演绎 <i>Men of War</i> 的战术战斗——融合真实的操作机制、电影化的镜头以及纯粹、强烈的战场沉浸感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/327130/extras/aafc8a2c27b59dcc7ab11a7cb8587ccb.poster.avif?t=1764074467\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/327130/extras/aafc8a2c27b59dcc7ab11a7cb8587ccb.webm?t=1764074467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/327130/extras/aafc8a2c27b59dcc7ab11a7cb8587ccb.mp4?t=1764074467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >功能</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>五个全新的单人 skirmish 任务</strong>，完全围绕坦克战展开：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>USA – “Dison”</strong>：M4A3E2(76) Jumbo、M26 Pershing、M26E4 Super Pershing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Germany – “Battle for Caen”</strong>：Panther、Jagdpanther、Veteran Tiger</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Commonwealth – “Wadi Akarit”</strong>：Comet I (A34)、M4A4 Firefly、Churchill Mk VII</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Soviet Union – “Tarnopol”</strong>：SU-100、KV-85、IS-2</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Japanese Empire – “Huon”</strong>：Chi-To、Chi-Ri、Ho-Ri I</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>完整第三人称直接操控</strong>——手动驾驶、瞄准与射击，获得全面沉浸感</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单位老兵（经验）系统</strong>，奖励高水平操作与长期生存</p></li><li><p class=\